# 条件判断与选择：{.nextsteps }
<style>
.nextsteps {
  color: #fff;
  background-color: #159957;
  background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, #A100FFFF 0%, #71C4FFFF 100%);
  padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
}
</style>

- if (condition) true_action

- if (condition) true_action else false_action

如果*condition*为真，执行*true_action*，否则执行*false_action*


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
x <- 85# mark of test
if (x > 90) {
    "A"
  } else if (x > 80) {
    "B"
  } else if (x > 50) {
    "C"
  } else {
    "F"
  }
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
[1] "B"
```


:::
:::




# 向量化的条件判断{.nextsteps }

基于向量的条件判断可以用*ifelse()*


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
x <- 1:10
ifelse(x %% 2 == 0, "even", "odd")
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
 [1] "odd"  "even" "odd"  "even" "odd"  "even" "odd"  "even" "odd"  "even"
```


:::
:::


# 向量化的条件判断2{.nextsteps }

基于向量的条件判断也可以用*dplyr::case_when()*


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
x <- 85# mark of test
dplyr::case_when(
x > 90~ "A",
x > 80~ "B",
x > 60~ "C",
is.na(x)~ "缺考",
T~"F"
)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
[1] "B"
```


:::
:::




# switch结构：{.nextsteps }

switch结构主要用于多条件判断,但不适用于数值型数据的比较判断，主要用于字符型数据


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
x <- "a"
 switch(x,
    a = "option 1",
    b = "option 2",
    c = "option 3",
    stop("Invalid `x` value")
  )
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
[1] "option 1"
```


:::
:::



# for循环：{.nextsteps }

for循环是在向量的基础上执行迭代运算，基本用法如：for (item in vector) perform_action



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
for (i in 1:3) {
  print(i)
}
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
[1] 1
[1] 2
[1] 3
```


:::

```{.r .cell-code}
for (i in 1:10) {
  if (i < 3) 
    next#跳过本条循环，进入下次

  print(i)

  if (i >= 5)
    break# 结束循环
}
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
[1] 3
[1] 4
[1] 5
```


:::
:::



# for循环的注意事项：{.nextsteps }

- 如果要产生新数据，记得提前分配数据收集结构  


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
means <- c(1, 50, 20)
out <- as.list(1:length(means))
# out <- vector("list", length(means))
for (i in 1:length(means)) {
  out[[i]] <- rnorm(10, means[[i]])
}
```
:::



-   seq_along(x) 在循环中更严谨 


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
means <- c()
out <- vector("list", length(means))
for (i in seq_along(means)) {
  out[[i]] <- rnorm(10, means[[i]])
}
```
:::



# 其他循环函数：{.nextsteps }
- while(condition) action: 执行 action while condition 为真

- repeat(action): 多次重复 action  (直到遇到break的条件)   


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
i <- 0
while (i<5) 
{
  print("I'm happy")
  i=i+1
}
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
[1] "I'm happy"
[1] "I'm happy"
[1] "I'm happy"
[1] "I'm happy"
[1] "I'm happy"
```


:::

```{.r .cell-code}
i <- 0
repeat {
  print("Hi")
  i <- i + 1
  if (i > 4)
    break
}
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
[1] "Hi"
[1] "Hi"
[1] "Hi"
[1] "Hi"
[1] "Hi"
```


:::
:::
